cles by studying the singly\nheavy baryons through various imperfect symmetries among them. We obtain an\nincidental conjecture that the lifetime and width may be quantized for the\nparticles existing in our realistic world as\n\\begin{equation*}M\\tau=n\\hbar/2~~~{\\rm{and}}~~~M/\\Gamma=n/2\\,,~~~n=1,2,3\\cdots\\,.\\end{equation*}\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 22 Feb 2023 19:30:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-24"}
