tages of\nthe complex-valued operations, the dual-path processing, and the joint-training\ntargets. Compared to the previous models, D2Former achieves state-of-the-art\nresults on the VoiceBank+Demand benchmark with the smallest model size of 0.87M\nparameters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 23 Feb 2023 07:43:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-24"}
