ization of additional point cloud information to\naccurately predict stable simulations where existing Graph Network Simulators\nfail.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 23 Feb 2023 09:06:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 7 Mar 2023 15:01:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-08"}
