 model-based and deep unfolded\ncounterparts with very low complexity and a fast run time. For example, in a\nsimulation with 128 transmit antennas, it attains a slightly higher spectral\nefficiency than the Riemannian manifold scheme, but over 1000 times faster and\nwith a complexity reduction of more than by a factor of six (6).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 23 Feb 2023 14:10:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-24"}
